The paper discusses meta-learning, which is a subarea of machine learning, and transfer learning, which is widely applied in complex tasks such as image classification, machine translation, and speech recognition. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
